text: "Money for Nothing/Beverly Hillbillies*" is a song by "Weird Al" Yankovic. It is a parody of "Money for Nothing" by Dire Straits and a cover of The Beverly Hillbillies theme song. It was featured in the movie UHF. ==References== Category:"Weird Al" Yankovic songs Category:Parodies Category:1989 songs
title: Money for Nothing/Beverly Hillbillies*
